Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟小不點人類無聊的一天又要開始了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅她還沒說早安哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  天亮了  不把眼睛睜開的話會被罵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直不醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是因為跟水銀燈打鬥  有哪裡故障了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小雛就不懂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就沒辦法了的說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就代替真紅  讓你們當我的僕從的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要當你的僕從啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個壞心眼人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼那麼激動的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是比較喜歡真紅的說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少胡說八道  我才不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「夢」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  我們家拒絕推銷員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近上門推銷的業務員  花樣還真是多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  發生火災了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼  原來是鬧鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是火災警鈴響了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家有裝火災警鈴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅還沒醒來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  紀  怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  關於神奇人偶的事  我也完全不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們實在太天真了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本是小事一樁的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  你的意思是你有辦法讓真紅醒來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有辦法的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當給她能力的媒介遇到了危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶就會有反應的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要丟下去了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是沒有醒來的跡象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就怪了的說  那就製造更大的危機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死人的  這樣一定會死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這個洞是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  你幹什麼多管閒事的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼人偶  你早就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了的說  這樣她就會醒來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  醒一醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅她不醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  真紅  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的說  怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地道的人偶推理劇場  一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是庫庫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  是庫庫偵探哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要讓庫庫動起來  真紅一定會醒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有純才能讓庫庫動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  真紅  謝謝你長期以來的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的  我想請你幫忙搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛睜開一下好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是受到誰的威脅  不敢開口說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為害羞  什麼話都不敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說  我們怎麼會知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  我上課的時候  也會想想看有沒有什麼好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要放棄  一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算少了「一隻」  可以稍微安靜一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小不點人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  純一定會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道有多久  沒有露出過那種表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的人偶師「羅真」所製作的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「活的人偶」的最高傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有人親眼看過  是否真的存在還是個疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論怎麼查  寫的都是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我記得以前在網站上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有人知道薔薇少女的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你是指那個薔薇少女嗎？)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我聽說那只是謠傳耶)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我也聽說過那是騙人的)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你真的相信啊  怎麼可能存在呢)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上就存在啊  就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  你在睡午覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個差勁的傢伙的說  都這種時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去  真紅會變成怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會繼續作夢的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶只要陷入深沉的睡眠  就會開始作夢的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢到以人偶的身份誕生  在漫長歲月中經歷的無數邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會夢到在記憶彼方的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有突然到訪的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連死都不被允許  永遠的沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全動彈不得  被一片漆黑籠罩的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望和期待  愉悅和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直重複夢見身為人偶  所感受到的所有記憶的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是亂編的故事  我記得書名是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去陪在真紅的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論誰來都不能出來哦  聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是令人火大的小不點的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)}人偶的歷史\N薔薇人偶\N創作人偶全集\NDoll's Rosa\N人偶師的世界\NRozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B6  B7
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的書沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為館內要改建  移去別的地方保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是附近的中學  你應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻田那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎？  那個櫻田啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了  不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓的力量  是從真紅那裡分來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅不在的話  她的力量會消失的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果是真紅的僕從  就要快點想想辦法的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那個超迷你的腦袋  好好想個辦法的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個沒用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我…本來就沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連雛莓都睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的很沒有用的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直關在自己房裡的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  要不要吃飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你聊一聊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我自言自語好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上看到你認真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起了小時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？  就是我弄丟布偶娃娃的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常努力做了一個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我真的好驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒想到你竟然能一個人就能做出布偶娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我認為  只要你願意什麼事都辦得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！我不是說過很多次了  我不想聽這種安慰話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是個沒用的傢伙  連學校都不敢進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒救了  只能這樣關在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話就快點滾出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說  純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅真的很喜歡你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅喜歡我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的太棒了  純
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指  彷彿彈奏著美妙的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要晨練嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想打了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上門是鎖著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要到學校來  為什麼不穿制服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要進去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好老師叫我來這裡找資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  雛莓也睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也不是這個原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…少女  這是德文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來記載的事情  是關於人偶師薔薇的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在此鄭重聲明  真偽無法判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓來我家的時候我很好奇  也來查過這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那關於修理的方法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不太清楚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  大概是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書不能借回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看就要趕快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的辦法…修理…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託…試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「Natureller Geist」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈？  居然說要拜託那種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人工精靈  你知道怎麼叫他出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問那個壞心眼人偶  可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏葉  你在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有人在  你知道後門怎麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  抱…抱歉啊  還讓你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這麼晚才叫我起床
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不管用的僕從呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微動腦筋想一想  就知道該怎麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡  人家擔心得要命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你怎麼滿臉通紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還是向你說聲謝謝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算睡到什麼時候？  快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  快去端茶來給我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼要我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個僕從很囉嗦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過了  這是你的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心腸果然還是迷你尺寸的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點起床
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅醒來之後  你突然變得很有精神的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂講！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  真紅  還不能讓你壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你變成廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點擔心那根樹枝伸展的情況的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在的話  應該就能把樹枝修剪得很美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許已經沒有互相瞭解的一天了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這麼悲傷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:24:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你心愛的雙胞胎妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這只薔薇戒指發誓吧
